scaling

loading the manual scales for Refseq body 2nd half:

data("Refseq_pc_g2k_q1_second_half_body_scales", package = 'arsRtools')

scales relative to PROMPT body 0 to +500

inputs <- dplyr::filter(bin_values, ab=='Input') %>%
    dplyr::select(id, rel_pos, sample_name, value) %>%
    dplyr::rename(used_input = sample_name, Input = value)

ips <- dplyr::filter(bin_values, ab=='PolII') %>%
    dplyr::select(id, siRNA, ab, main_run, run, rel_pos, sample_name, used_input, value) %>%
    dplyr::rename(ChIP = value)

d <- left_join(ips, inputs) %>%
    dplyr::select(id, siRNA, ab, main_run, run, rel_pos, ChIP, Input) %>%
    left_join(., Refseq_pc_g2k_q1_second_half_body_scales) %>%
    mutate(scaled_input = Input*input_scale_factor,
           BGSub_ChIP = ChIP-scaled_input)
min_rel_pos <- 0
max_rel_pos <- 500

region_values <- d %>%
      dplyr::select(-chip_scale_factor) %>%
      filter(rel_pos >= min_rel_pos, rel_pos <= max_rel_pos) %>%
      group_by(siRNA, ab, main_run, run, rel_pos) %>%
      summarize(mean_BGSub_ChIP = mean(BGSub_ChIP)) %>%
      group_by(siRNA, ab, main_run, run) %>%
      summarize(chip_scale_factor = 1/mean(mean_BGSub_ChIP))
    
d %<>%
      dplyr::select(-chip_scale_factor) %>%
      left_join(., region_values)
    
PROMPT0to500_region_scaled <- d %>%
    mutate(scaled_BGSub_ChIP = BGSub_ChIP * chip_scale_factor,
           siRNA = factor(siRNA, levels=c('siARS2', 'siFFL', 'siRRP40', 'siZ18')),
           run = factor(run, levels=c('CI62', 'CI63',
                                      'MA72_z18', 'MA73_z18',
                                      'MA72_rrp40', 'MA73_rrp40')),
           main_run = factor(main_run, levels=c('CI siARS2',
                                                'MA siZ18',
                                                'MA siRRP40'))) %>%
    dplyr::select(id, main_run, run, siRNA, rel_pos, scaled_BGSub_ChIP)

ChIPseq profile plot

meta_line_plot <- function(scaled_BGsub) {
  scaled_BGsub %>%
  group_by(siRNA, main_run, run, rel_pos) %>%
  summarize(mean_value=mean(scaled_BGSub_ChIP)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  group_by(siRNA, main_run, rel_pos) %>%
  mutate(upper = max(mean_value), lower = min(mean_value), center = mean(mean_value)) %>%
ggplot(., aes(x=rel_pos, y=center, color=siRNA)) +
  geom_ribbon(aes(ymin=lower, ymax=upper, fill=siRNA), alpha=1 ) +
  facet_grid(.~main_run) +
  lineplot_theme +
  xlim(-2000,5000) +
  xlab(paste0('bp to ', biotype, ' ', anchor))
}
meta_line_plot(PROMPT0to500_region_scaled)  +
  ylab('PROMPT 0tp500 scaled values')

Wilcoxon FDR plot

wilcox_travel_ratio <- function(scaled_BGsub, wilcox_alternative = 'greater') {
  scaled_BGsub %>%
    mutate(KD = ifelse(siRNA == 'siFFL', 'siFFL', 'KD')) %>%
    select(id, KD, main_run, run, rel_pos, scaled_BGSub_ChIP) %>%
    group_by(id, KD, main_run, run, rel_pos) %>%
    spread(KD, scaled_BGSub_ChIP) %>%
    group_by(main_run, rel_pos) %>%
    do(tidy(wilcox.test(.$KD, .$siFFL, alternative = wilcox_alternative, paired=T))) %>%
    group_by(main_run) %>% #altPROMPTtive use fdr using all samples ie ungroup() here??
    mutate(fdr = p.adjust(p.value, method='fdr'))
}
line_plot_sigtest <- function(sigtest) {
  ggplot(sigtest, aes(x=rel_pos, y=-log10(fdr))) +
    geom_line() +
    facet_grid(.~main_run) +
  lineplot_theme +
  xlim(-2000,5000) +
    geom_hline(yintercept = 1, color='orange', linetype=2) +
  xlab(paste0('bp to ', biotype, ' ', anchor))
} 
wilcox_travel_ratio(PROMPT0to500_region_scaled) %>%
line_plot_sigtest(.)

heatmaps logFC

data('RNAseq_logFC_heatmap_theme', package='arsRtools')
log_ratio <- function(scaled_BGsub) {
  min_val <- min(scaled_BGsub$scaled_BGSub_ChIP[scaled_BGsub$scaled_BGSub_ChIP>0])
  
  scaled_BGsub %>%
  mutate(KD = ifelse(siRNA == 'siFFL', 'siFFL', 'KD'),
         scaled_BGSub_ChIP = ifelse(scaled_BGSub_ChIP <= 0, min_val, scaled_BGSub_ChIP+min_val)) %>%
  dplyr::select(id, rel_pos, KD, main_run, scaled_BGSub_ChIP) %>%
  group_by(KD, id, main_run, KD, rel_pos) %>%
  summarize(scaled_BGSub_ChIP = mean(scaled_BGSub_ChIP)) %>%
  spread(KD, scaled_BGSub_ChIP) %>%
  mutate(log2_ratio = log2(KD)-log2(siFFL) )
}


PROMPT0to500_scaled_BGsub_ratio <- log_ratio(PROMPT0to500_region_scaled)
heatmap_ratio <- function(scaled_ratio_df) {
  
  row_order <- scaled_ratio_df %>%
    filter(!is.na(log2_ratio),
         rel_pos > -2000, rel_pos < 5000) %>%
    group_by(id) %>% 
    summarize(total_value = sum(log2_ratio)) %>% 
    ungroup %>% 
    arrange(total_value) %$% 
    id
  
  scaled_ratio_df %>%
    filter(!is.na(log2_ratio),
         rel_pos > -2000, rel_pos < 5000) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
  mutate(log2_ratio = case_when(.$log2_ratio > 2 ~ 2,
                                .$log2_ratio < -2 ~ -2,
                                TRUE ~ .$log2_ratio),
         id = factor(id, levels=row_order)) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x=rel_pos, y=id, fill=log2_ratio)) +
  geom_raster(interpolate = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(.~main_run) +
  RNAseq_logFC_heatmap_theme  +
    theme(axis.text.y = element_blank()) +
  xlab(paste0('bp to ', biotype, ' ', anchor))
}
heatmap_ratio(PROMPT0to500_scaled_BGsub_ratio)
